350Z/G35 people:

My dome light suddenly doesn't work.

The door pins work because the key- in chime and headlight chime still know when a door is open.

I can tap the headlights and they work (different circuit), but the circuit that comes on w the doors opening or the unlock isn't operating.

Anyone have this occur before and know what the fix is?

Edit/solved!:

Bingo. 
The cluster side controls MUST be plugged into the oem gauge pod in order for the dome light to work.

Fixed. ❤️😎🤝

Two thin gauge strips of butyl sound deadener from Gtmat was enough to cut the resonance out of the thin flat door skin panel.

Remember..
"dynamat" is not for road/ tire / gravel or exhaust noise.. And it doesn't have to be laid thick, nor laid across the whole panel.
It simply changes the resonance hz and the amount of energy it takes to make a panel buzz.
In total I added back  0.65 lbs per door  in order to have a nice solid sound and feel when they close.. And that's perfectly acceptable to me. 

(total weight with the material was 13.6 lbs )

Bags are for AIRING out flat, not for lifting.
AIR CUPS leave an otherwise completely static spring in place on your damper.
It lifts quickly, and only when needed.

(Airbags present a multitude of issues when it comes to riding low/low pressure, as well as any attempts at damping the now continuously variable air spring.

They are great for laying your car out in a parking lot, but imo, most fast cars that look good flat.. still look good a few inches up and driveable.) 

Set your car low and static, lift it when needed. Problem solved. 
You'll never be stranded or stuck from a leaking line, bad ground or a popped bag, it's a much lighter system, and it's far more simple to install and use.
And..... your car will still handle CORRECTLY.
" Idk, but it FEELS like it rides good tho?" is what u tell yourself w bags..been there.. and for some, that's fine... I love using  bags on my larger, slower cruiser  cars...

But for others, the Air Cup front axle lift is the welcomed solution we've been waiting for...
Most folks just aren't aware it exists or what it really does. 
🤷🤷😎👌❤️
